  </tr>
  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>wdaher's idea of changing the filename is a very good idea, and not one that has
come up in previous discussions of this bug.

I like that a lot, and will take that tack when fixing it.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
   <th><a href="msg2502">msg2502 (view)</a></th>
   <th>Author: jesstess</th>
   <th>Date: 2011-09-20.03:48:22</th>
